      <abstract>
        <p>In this paper we propose the synthesis of (<italic>E</italic>)-4-methyl-N-(3,4,5-trimethoxybenzylidene) benzenamine in different ways and compare of the way of synthesize it. As a result, microwave irradiation is the simple way to synthesis this Schiff base.</p>
